column4: select fr.infologic.stocks.utils.persistence.scalars.scalarqtemttmvt ( a.prod.ik, a.lot.ik, a.datprepsaisie, a.datprep, a.qteubase, a.qteuelem, a.poidsnet, a.poidsbrut, a.poidstheo, a.longueur, a.largeur, a.hauteur, a.surface, a.volume, a.volumecontenu, a.temps, a.qteusousembal, a.qteuelemappro, a.qteusurembal, a.qteulogissuppl1, a.qteulogissuppl2, a.mttnet, a.mttrist, a.mttfrais1, a.mttfrais2, a.mttfrais3, a.mttfrais4, a.mttfrais5 ) from fr.infologic.stocks.gestion.modele.mvtrealise as a where ( a.prod.ik in ( collection0_ ) ) and ( a.lieu.ik in ( collection1_ ) ) and (a.chrono, a.lieu.ik, a.prod.ik, a.lot.ik) in (select max(filterindermvtacfab.chrono), filterindermvtacfab.lieu.ik, filterindermvtacfab.prod.ik, filterindermvtacfab.lot.ik from fr.infologic.stocks.gestion.modele.mvtrealise as filterindermvtacfab where 1 = 1 and filterindermvtacfab.dossierinfo.dosres = p1 and filterindermvtacfab.flagannule = p2 and filterindermvtacfab.signe = p3 and filterindermvtacfab.sens = p4 and 1 = 1 group by filterindermvtacfab.lieu.ik, filterindermvtacfab.prod.ik, filterindermvtacfab.lot.ik ) and a.dossierinfo.dosres = p5

select fr.infologic.stocks.utils.persistence.scalars.deuxiksdate ( a.lot.ik, a.unitlogis.ik, min ( a.datprepsaisie ) ) from fr.infologic.stocks.gestion.modele.mvtrealise as a where a.flagannule = p1 and a.signe = p2 and ( a.prod.ik in ( collection0_ ) ) and ( a.lieu.ik in ( collection1_ ) ) and a.dossierinfo.dosres = p3 group by a.lot.ik,a.unitlogis.ik

select fr.infologic.stocks.utils.persistence.scalars.deuxiksdate ( a.lieu.ik, a.prod.ik, max ( a.datprepsaisie ) ) from fr.infologic.stocks.gestion.modele.mvtrealise as a where ( a.lieu.ik in ( collection0_ ) ) and a.flagannule = p1 and ( a.prod.ik in ( collection1_ ) or a.prod.ik in ( collection2_ ) ) group by a.lieu.ik,a.prod.ik
